<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2024-01-13 09:10:03.661611</lastBuildDate><item><title>It is what it is...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9qObQgC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CpSayoZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After two years of being treated as he deserved, tiny octopus said, enough is enough.

Just a quick edit. Tiny octopus' former job was a good one, which is why he said he was getting treated as he deserved. The pay was decent, the benefits were good for the corporate world, and the supervisor was a good chap. It was just too good of an opportunity to move to the civil service side with the benefits, union, pension and the PSLF program.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jHKNpkn.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Went from contractor to full on civilian. GS-11 now with an increased step because he was recruited. Pay is about the same, but am now union with much better benefits. And a pension. Woo!

Told the tiniers that their dad is now unemployed. At least until Tuesday when he steps onto the base as a CIV instead of a CTR.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9qObQgC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TinyOctopus]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Because they're worth it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5iEgTxi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0XQeNKD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5iEgTxi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GorgeousGeorgieous]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I guess he was coming tonight, just a bit too early</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SSfC4PC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dq2cE9q.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SSfC4PC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Basti2202]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Me too Emma, me too! Lmfao</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2RhCWo3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GtjpUWt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2RhCWo3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DumpingSh1tandBeingKind2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>More life at sea.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/no6xW9w</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6Hvrh9g.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/no6xW9w</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dickwitfo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I Want to Believe... in my knitting skills!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/z8vsL6a</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dfcYRNq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I wrote more on my insta: thread_and_roses, but long story short - I just finished my first colorwork knitting project! I probably should've gone with an easier pattern for my first, but rarely do I take the easy way out when it comes to crafting XD</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B04kvWi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's super warm, too! I'd wear it every day if I weren't a farm worker lol</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/z8vsL6a</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[lunacane]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Improvise, adapt, overcome</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pgSBplF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RF5S702.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pgSBplF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ImpatientMoth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Vandalay Industries</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rB9AfzJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gray9uX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rB9AfzJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[astronomypictures]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm doing the things.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Aq5Xdjx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rtk0a26.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>FP edit: Holy Canolies guys thanks for the support and the love, y'all are way awesome! I'll keep it quick here, but some have asked why I went. Well, I used to be a self employed salesman. Unfortunately, what I sold was illegal (various narcotics) and I was contributing to the delinquency of society. Arrested in 2018 for delivery of controlled substance and possession of felony weight of controlled substance. Given a 5-8 sentence, I did the crime and boy did I do the time. Twas not all bad, learned a bunch of cool stuff about myself and never once dropped the soap. Again, thanks for the love and support. Started my job as a line cook at a badass restaurant in town making more than I probably deserve. Ready to save up some bucks and get myself out of this homeless shelter. My whole experience has been extremely humbling and Im starting over, it's super sweet! Be nice to each other.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Aq5Xdjx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BlukupReborn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Also CNN, Fox, and Sky.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YLDuH1e</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XXEn5WZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YLDuH1e</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Esimerkiksi]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tax the Rich</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/M3oV2oC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RGcYh5P.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ehjQMvR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Then Eat em!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/M3oV2oC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ssumner13]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I still believe tumblr can become the next pdf</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4VWZcEW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/00fMjHu.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m2vHOrA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bBj111K.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://qz.com/708295/yahoos-grand-plan-for-tumblr-was-to-turn-it-into-the-next-generation-pdf</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.