ATA[dickwitfo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ha!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/h065gHq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WzWFFuO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/h065gHq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Learning how to smile again... my 1st before pic is to disgusting to show</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dQM6LMC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1mRIwUZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Trying them on before surgery</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9Juc4RK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Right after surgery. Realizing i dont know how to smile showing teeth or smiling at all after years of covering face ( hence the beard mustache hiding it )</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0Lla7mr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Still learning ... still very painful</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gnJp3Ds.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The 1st smile i had in decades i was proud of ... im so lucky i was able to afford it. Being able to smile changes every moment of your life. I was so scared to do it ( phobia of dentist and being put under ) it was so worth it ... just cant wait to eat solid food again ... please dont hate to much for selfies. And please take care of your mouth it fucking sucks going through this. Just dont hesitate to ends justify the means</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/dQM6LMC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Leoso0]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>a thing of beauty…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/goeeTNR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XGnWWl5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/goeeTNR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aerrorfree]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wanted for illegally operating a motor while being smol</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/melFgbh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fOGPL1i.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/melFgbh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tampacl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>City of St Paul keeping it real</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vXWAv4K</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BlIRou9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vXWAv4K</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AllAnusMorissette]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>New Year’s Resolution: Learn more about my mom</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CmRhR6X</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rHM4TMp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sorry if this post is too serious. She passed away shortly after this image, in 2009, after being the victim of a murder-suicide. For so long, I subconsciously viewed her as some mythical figure and even forgot I had the capacity to ask questions about her. I am now 21, and in 2024 I am going to have deep conversations with my family and those who knew her about who she was in life</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CmRhR6X</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[naturalselectn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good morning!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FwnfHn6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aLyMONA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rM2qZkB.gif" style="max-widt